Vlocity Insurance Group Benefits Census Management for Quoting

An underwriter, broker, or sales executive can upload a census to a quote to calibrate the pricing of group benefits products. The Vlocity Insurance Census Lightning web component helps manage census data on a Quote or Census record page.

Select a Group Benefits Census
A census gathers and maintains member and dependent data for accurate quotes.

Rerate a Group Benefits Quote After Every Census Change
To keep a quote accurate, rerate the quote every time the census data changes.
